HL_SCM_MATDOC_DELTA_SQL.@EndUserText.label: Material Movements - Delta and Historical
HL_SCM_MATDOC_DELTA_SQL.@DataWarehouse.tableFunction.script:
/**
    * return select "Column1","Column2" from "table";
*/

TAB_MATDOC_1 = 

SELECT
A."DATE_SQL" as CALDAY,
B.MATNR as MATERIAL, 
B.WERKS as PLANT,
B."0BASE_UOM" as BASE_UOM,
SUM ("0RECTOTSTCK") as RECTOTSTCK_DELTA,
SUM ("0ISSTOTSTCK") as ISSTOTSTCK_DELTA,
SUM ("0RECVALSTCK") as RECVALSTCK_DELTA,
SUM ("0ISSVALSTCK") as ISSVALSTCK_DELTA,
SUM ("0RECVS_VAL") as RECVS_VAL_DELTA,
SUM ("0ISSVS_VAL") as ISSVS_VAL_DELTA,

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0RECTOTSTCK") ELSE 0 END as "RECTOTSTCK_CALDAY",
CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0ISSTOTSTCK") ELSE 0 END as "ISSTOTSTCK_CALDAY",

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0RECVALSTCK") ELSE 0 END as "RECVALSTCK_CALDAY",
CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0ISSVALSTCK") ELSE 0 END as "ISSVALSTCK_CALDAY",

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0RECVS_VAL") ELSE 0 END as "RECVS_VAL_CALDAY",
CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0ISSVS_VAL") ELSE 0 END as "ISSVS_VAL_CALDAY"


FROM "SAP.TIME.VIEW_DIMENSION_DAY" AS A 
LEFT JOIN "HL_SCM_INVENTORY_BAL_01" AS B 
ON B."0CALDAY" <= A."DATE_SAP"

WHERE B."0RECORDTP" = '0' 
       AND A."DATE_SQL" <= CURRENT_DATE 
       AND A.YEAR>= YEAR(ADD_YEARS(CURRENT_DATE,-3))  
GROUP BY 
A."DATE_SQL" ,
B."0CALDAY",
B.MATNR,
B.WERKS,
B."0BASE_UOM"
;


TAB_MATDOC_2 = 

SELECT
A."DATE_SQL" as CALDAY,

B.MATNR as MATERIAL, 
B.WERKS as PLANT,
--B."0CALDAY" AS CALDAY,
B."0BASE_UOM" as BASE_UOM,

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" > A."DATE_SAP" THEN
SUM ("0RECTOTSTCK") ELSE 0 END as RECTOTSTCK_HIST ,

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" > A."DATE_SAP" THEN
SUM ("0ISSTOTSTCK") ELSE 0 END as ISSTOTSTCK_HIST,

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" > A."DATE_SAP" THEN
SUM ("0RECVALSTCK") ELSE 0 END as RECVALSTCK_HIST ,

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" > A."DATE_SAP" THEN
SUM ("0ISSVALSTCK") ELSE 0 END as ISSVALSTCK_HIST,

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" > A."DATE_SAP" THEN
SUM ("0RECVS_VAL") ELSE 0 END as RECVS_VAL_HIST ,

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" > A."DATE_SAP" THEN
SUM ("0ISSVS_VAL") ELSE 0 END as ISSVS_VAL_HIST,

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0RECTOTSTCK") ELSE 0 END as "RECTOTSTCK_CALDAY",
CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0ISSTOTSTCK") ELSE 0 END as "ISSTOTSTCK_CALDAY",

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0RECVALSTCK") ELSE 0 END as "RECVALSTCK_CALDAY",
CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0ISSVALSTCK") ELSE 0 END as "ISSVALSTCK_CALDAY",

CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0RECVS_VAL") ELSE 0 END as "RECVS_VAL_CALDAY",
CASE WHEN B."0CALDAY" = A."DATE_SQL" THEN   SUM("0ISSVS_VAL") ELSE 0 END as "ISSVS_VAL_CALDAY"

FROM "SAP.TIME.VIEW_DIMENSION_DAY" AS A 
LEFT JOIN "HL_SCM_INVENTORY_BAL_01" AS B 
ON B."0CALDAY" >= A."DATE_SAP"

WHERE B."0RECORDTP" = '2' AND B."BWART" > '000' 
AND A."DATE_SQL" <= CURRENT_DATE
AND A.YEAR>= YEAR(ADD_YEARS(CURRENT_DATE,-3))  

GROUP BY 
A."DATE_SQL" ,
A."DATE_SAP",
B."0CALDAY",
B.MATNR,
B.WERKS,
B."0BASE_UOM"
;

TAB_MATDOC_SUMMARY = 
SELECT CALDAY, MATERIAL, PLANT,BASE_UOM,
       RECTOTSTCK_DELTA , 
       ISSTOTSTCK_DELTA, 
       0.0 AS RECTOTSTCK_HIST,
       0.0 AS ISSTOTSTCK_HIST,
       RECTOTSTCK_CALDAY,
       ISSTOTSTCK_CALDAY,
       
       RECVALSTCK_DELTA , 
       ISSVALSTCK_DELTA, 
       0.0 AS RECVALSTCK_HIST,
       0.0 AS ISSVALSTCK_HIST,
       RECVALSTCK_CALDAY,
       ISSVALSTCK_CALDAY,
       
       RECVS_VAL_DELTA , 
       ISSVS_VAL_DELTA, 
       0.0 AS RECVS_VAL_HIST,
       0.0 AS ISSVS_VAL_HIST,
       RECVS_VAL_CALDAY,
       ISSVS_VAL_CALDAY
       
       FROM :TAB_MATDOC_1  
       UNION ALL
       
SELECT CALDAY, MATERIAL, PLANT,  
      BASE_UOM,
       0.0 as RECTOTSTCK_DELTA , 
       0.0 as ISSTOTSTCK_DELTA, 
       RECTOTSTCK_HIST ,
       ISSTOTSTCK_HIST,
       RECTOTSTCK_CALDAY,
       ISSTOTSTCK_CALDAY,
       
       0.0 as RECVALSTCK_DELTA , 
       0.0 as ISSVALSTCK_DELTA, 
       RECVALSTCK_HIST,
       ISSVALSTCK_HIST,
       RECVALSTCK_CALDAY,
       ISSVALSTCK_CALDAY,
       
       0.0 as RECVS_VAL_DELTA , 
       0.0 as ISSVS_VAL_DELTA, 
       RECVS_VAL_HIST,
       ISSVS_VAL_HIST,
       RECVS_VAL_CALDAY,
       ISSVS_VAL_CALDAY
       
       FROM :TAB_MATDOC_2;        
       
RETURN
SELECT 
    SUM(RECTOTSTCK_DELTA) as RECTOTSTCK_DELTA , 
    SUM(ISSTOTSTCK_DELTA) as ISSTOTSTCK_DELTA, 
    CALDAY, 
    MATERIAL, 
    PLANT, 
    BASE_UOM,
    SUM(RECTOTSTCK_HIST) as RECTOTSTCK_HIST , 
    SUM(ISSTOTSTCK_HIST) as ISSTOTSTCK_HIST,
    SUM(RECTOTSTCK_CALDAY) as RECTOTSTCK_CALDAY ,
    SUM(ISSTOTSTCK_CALDAY) as ISSTOTSTCK_CALDAY,
    SUM(RECVALSTCK_DELTA) as RECVALSTCK_DELTA,
    SUM(ISSVALSTCK_DELTA) as ISSVALSTCK_DELTA,
    SUM(RECVALSTCK_HIST) as RECVALSTCK_HIST,
    SUM(ISSVALSTCK_HIST) as ISSVALSTCK_HIST,
    SUM(RECVALSTCK_CALDAY) as RECVALSTCK_CALDAY,
    SUM(ISSVALSTCK_CALDAY) as ISSVALSTCK_CALDAY,
       SUM(RECVS_VAL_DELTA) as RECVS_VAL_DELTA,
       SUM(ISSVS_VAL_DELTA) as ISSVS_VAL_DELTA,
       SUM(RECVS_VAL_HIST) as RECVS_VAL_HIST,
       SUM(ISSVS_VAL_HIST) as ISSVS_VAL_HIST,
       SUM(RECVS_VAL_CALDAY) as RECVS_VAL_CALDAY,
       SUM(ISSVS_VAL_CALDAY) as ISSVS_VAL_CALDAY
       
       FROM :TAB_MATDOC_SUMMARY
       GROUP BY 
       CALDAY, 
       MATERIAL, PLANT,  BASE_UOM
       ;
